2022 PH Election - Pasig City

Marcos won Pasig City by about 17%. Leni won big in the brgys in and around the Ortigas CBD, containing the subdivisions of Valle Verde and Green Meadows, and the Kapitolyo area. She lost to BBM in most of the areas east of C5.

2022 Philippine VP Election - Pasig City

Sara Duterte won Pasig City with almost 49% of the vote.

Kiko Pangilinan won 3 brgys (Kaptiloyo, San Antonio, Ugong) compared to Leni's 6. 

Tito Sotto was able to get 2nd place in 12 brgys.

2022 PH Election - Puerto Princesa City

In a flip from 2016, Marcos won Puerto Princesa City with about 55% of the vote. 

Robredo got 2nd place with 25% but failed to win a brgy in the city. 

Pacquiao was at 3rd place with  ~13% of the vote but won 4 brgys.
